title: Funniest/Most Insightful Comments Of The Week At Techdirt
description: This week, our first place winner on the insightful side is an anonymous comment about one detail in Google’s push for anti-open-internet regulation: Goody. Mandating porn ID and, by association, tying porn use with that ID. Sounds like Google is advocating for, among other things, government mandated collection of adults’ fetishes tied to their names. […]
